<ol>
<li>At least 18 years old.</li>
<li>Member of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints.</li>
<li>Volunteer does <span style="text-decoration: underline;">not</span> need to be a BYU-Idaho student.</li>
<li>Fluent in English. No second language skills needed.</li>
<li>Willing to spend 20&ndash;40 minutes, twice a week.</li>
<li>Access to high-speed Internet, webcam, and microphone.</li>
</ol>
<p><br /><br /></p>
